features: Global Compatibility for Worldwide Travel – The MOMAX travel adapter supports four plug types (A, O, C, and BF) and is compatible with outlets in over 200 countries, including the US, UK, Europe, and Australia. Whether you’re traveling for business or leisure, this adapter ensures you can easily plug in no matter where you go

Compact and Lightweight, Travel-Friendly – Weighing only 98g and 50% smaller than typical models (93*55*50mm), the MOMAX adapter is compact enough to fit into any bag without taking up precious space. Ideal for international trips, business meetings, or short training sessions. The retractable plug design ensures a hassle-free and space-saving experience

Dual AC Outlets for Charging Multiple Devices – With two AC outlets, you can charge multiple devices like your phone, tablet, and laptop at the same time, even when outlets are limited. The thoughtful outlet layout allows for large adapters to be plugged in without interference. Perfect for extended business trips or family vacations

Certified Safety for Peace of Mind – With ROHS, CE, and FCC certifications, the MOMAX adapter provides multiple safety protections, including overheat, overcurrent, overcharge, and short-circuit safeguards. A built-in 10A fuse adds extra protection, so you can feel confident that your devices are safe wherever you are

Note - This product does not have a voltage conversion function, so be sure to check the voltage before use. Appliances labeled as compatible with 100-250V are overseas specification appliances and therefore can be used without a transformer. We offer a 1-year warranty, so if you have any questions about our products, please let us know. We will endeavor to resolve the issue as soon as possible
description: Product Description Equipped with two AC outlets One of these is enough for a business trip or a trip! Two models can be charged at the same time in a batch, and the lack of power outlets can be solved. Outlets can be distributed in each direction so that two large adapters can be inserted at the same time without interfering with each other. (Note: power conversion only, no fast charging) Small and lightweight Compact and space-saving, half the size of a normal size. You can go to any country with just one of these! 2 AC power outlets Can charge two models at the same time, solving the problem of insufficient power outlets. Type A (U.S. logo): United States, Brazil, Cambodia, China, Colombia, Cuba, Haiti, Japan, Laos, Mexico, Panama, Philippines, Thailand, etc. Type O (AUS logo): American Samoa, Argentina, Australia, Cook Islands, East Timor, Fiji, Kiribati, Nauru, New Zealand, Okinawa, Samoa, Tonga, Uruguay, Vanuatu, etc. Type BF (British flag): UK, Hong Kong, Macau, Singapore, Malaysia, India, Vietnam, Kuwait, Bhutan, Kenya, Bahrain, Gambia and Nigeria. Type C (EU mark): Available in Germany, Italy, Switzerland, Holland, Denmark, Finland and other European countries as well as Korea and other countries.
